description:
Minor amendment to approved reserved matters consent ('Appearance' only) ref: P062805 dated 30/04/2007 to:
A] - increase the building heights of the 6-storey canalside east building by 728mm, 520mm, 575mm and 375mm respectively, including rearrangement of windows;
B] - increase the building heights of the 6-storey canalside west building by 875mm, 1075mm and 1020mm respectively, including rearrangement of windows;
C] - increase of the building height of the terrace houses to Dame Street by up to 595mm (creating stepped parapet);
D] - increase in the width of the CHP chimney;
E] - increase the building height of the single storey youth centre building by 235mm and insertion of new rear door/window; 
F] - increase the building height of the 4-storey workshop building by 415mm and 750mm and relocation of entrance; and
G] - provide a substation entrance at ground floor level to canalside east building, north elevation.
